title: NFL Combine Results and Impressions | The Dantasy Football Podcast
description:
From a hotel room in Indianapolis, Danny and Danny offer their initial takeaways from a star-studded NFL combine. We start by discussing Alabama quarterback Tua Tagovailoa’s promising medical examination, then break down the elite potential of guys like Alabama wide receiver Henry Ruggs III and Wisconsin running back Jonathan Taylor, and many more.
Hosts: Danny Heifetz and Danny Kelly
